{"id": "xos010", "name": "Cam_Arc_702_07_22", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_OBS_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos1001"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I tracked down the IP address of the anonymous mail I received a while ago.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "Hmm?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "The address is within A.R.C.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "So who is it?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "No matter how hard I try I can only get the IP address. Haven't run into an encryption this tough in a long time.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "Does our company really have someone like that?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Can't say it's impossible. People that come to work at A.R.C. are all extremely skilled. \n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "So this guy chose to hide his abilities, yet writes a letter like this to challenge you?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "The only possible candidate I can think of right now is the new advisor. I met him a few days ago.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "Oh. How was it?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "He's a complete a-hole. However, I might have to admit that he indeed has something special, or else the company would not give a non-regular employee access to so many things. \n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "He still thinks it's not enough though.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Regardless I will keep a keen eye on him. He is not someone you should overlook.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "OK.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Replay Ends]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_OBS_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos1001"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "この前のメールの発信源が掴めた。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "へぇ？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "A.R.C.内部から送られたものだ。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "誰だ？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "どんなに手を尽くしても、IPアドレスしか掴めない。ここまで手を焼くのは久しぶりだ。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "社内にそんなやつが？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "いないとは言い切れないだろ。A.R.C.に入ってくる人間はみんな超人的なレベルの奴らばかりなんだから。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "そいつは会社では本当の力を発揮しないくせに、こんなメールでお前を挑発してくると？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "今考えられるのは、あの新しく来た顧問だけだな。数日前に会った。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "あぁ。どうだった？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "いけ好かない奴だったよ。だが、確かにすごい人だ。でなければ、会社だって彼にあんなに多くの権限を与えたりしないだろ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "だが、本人はまだ不満みたいだ。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "とにかく、警戒しておくに越したことはない。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "あぁ。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[再生終了]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_OBS_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos1001"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我追蹤到之前那封匿名信的發信位址了。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是從 A.R.C. 內部發出來的。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "所以是誰？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我怎麼破也只能破解出位址而已，真的很久沒有看過這麼堅固的防壁了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "公司裡真的有這樣的人？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "不能保證沒有，能來 A.R.C. 工作的人，都有超乎常人的水準。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "然後這個人在公司不露真功夫，卻故意寫這種信挑戰你？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我現在唯一想到的可能就是那個新來的顧問，我前幾天跟他碰面了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯，如何？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是個討厭的傢伙，但也不得不承認他也許真的蠻厲害，不然公司不會對一個約聘開放那麼多權限。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "不過他好像覺得還不夠。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "總之我會特別盯緊他，他是個危險人物。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[播放結束]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_OBS_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos1001"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "저번에 익명으로 보낸 메일의 위치를 찾아냈어.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "A.R.C. 내부에서 발신한 거더군.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "그래서 누구인데?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "나도 이제 막 위치만 알아낸 것뿐이라고. 꽤 오랫동안 이렇게 견고하게 구축된 방화벽을 만나보질 못했는데.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "정말 회사 내부에 있는 사람인 거야?\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "확실하진 않지만, A.R.C.의 직원일 가능성이 크지. 메일 내용도, 방화벽도, 이미 일반인의 수준을 넘어섰어.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "그리고 일부러 증거를 남긴 것도 보면, 일부러 네게 도전하려는 뜻이 아닐까?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "현재 내가 생각해 봤을 때 딱 떠오르는 사람은 그 새로 왔다던 고문뿐이군. 며칠 전에도 한 번 만났었어.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "오. 어땠어?\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "꽤 마음에 안 드는 녀석이야. 하지만 그 사람이 대단하단 사실은 인정하지 않을 수 없어. 안 그랬으면 회사에서도 그 사람에게 그렇게나 많은 권한과 편의를 제공해 주지 않았겠지.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "하지만 그 사람은 그걸로는 성이 안 차 하는 것 같던데.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "어쨌든 특별히 주시해서 지켜볼 생각이야. 꽤 위험한 인물 같으니.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "응\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[재생 종료]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_OBS_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos1001"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我追蹤到之前那封匿名信的發信位址了。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是從 A.R.C. 內部發出來的。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "所以是誰？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我怎麼破也只能破解出位址而已，真的很久沒有看過這麼堅固的防壁了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "公司裡真的有這樣的人？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "不能保證沒有，能來 A.R.C. 工作的人，都有超乎常人的水準。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "然後這個人在公司不露真功夫，卻故意寫這種信挑戰你？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我現在唯一想到的可能就是那個新來的顧問，我前幾天跟他碰面了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯，如何？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是個討厭的傢伙，但也不得不承認他也許真的蠻厲害，不然公司不會對一個約聘開放那麼多權限。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "不過他好像覺得還不夠。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "總之我會特別盯緊他，他是個危險人物。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[播放結束]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["ARC_OBS_AMB"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "image", "attrs": ["xos1001"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我追踪到之前那封匿名信的发信位址了。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是从 A.R.C. 内部发出来的。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "所以是谁？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我怎么破也只能破解出位址而已，真的很久没有看过这么坚固的防壁了。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "公司里真的有这样的人？\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "不能保证没有，能来 A.R.C. 工作的人，都有超乎常人的水准。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "然后这个人在公司不露真功夫，却故意写这种信挑战你？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我现在唯一想到的可能就是那个新来的顾问，我前几天跟他碰面了。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯，如何？\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是个讨厌的家伙，但也不得不承认他也许真的蛮厉害，不然公司不会对一个约聘开放那么多权限。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "不过他好像觉得还不够。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "总之我会特别盯紧他，他是个危险人物。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Mark"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[播放结束]</i>"}]]}